{"tid":2334011,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"【Startup/創業討論區】想搞startup/創業既一齊入嚟傾下？","createTime":"2020-12-21T01:03:46.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-20T22:47:59.000Z","uid":385382,"like":4,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"8f3fd052d9b597208c46499b478e6ce55958b3be","tid":2334011,"uid":385382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T01:03:46.000Z","msg":"唔知有無其他人同我一樣，打工打到無咩希望，想趁年輕創下業<br />\n宜家日日上網research做功課，學好點搞startup然後諗做咩product<br />\n想睇下有冇同道中人既巴打絲打有興趣吹下水<br />\n有經驗/創緊業既可以講下自己啲advice，好似我咁仲FF緊既可以講下自己啲大計<br />\n如果遲啲大家有興趣 我可以share下我覺得有用既resources"},{"pid":"49a49ad397c85ce9a792e216227d420685072141","tid":2334011,"uid":10608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T01:05:59.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"7d16455cacf4c9619ae01f57b84bd178da2ce3e6","tid":2334011,"uid":838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T02:47:41.000Z","msg":"老闆只能有一個"},{"pid":"b07abfe5bbc4add4a62c23039330e5f99c977ee6","tid":2334011,"uid":122231,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T03:00:51.000Z","msg":"記住<br />\n<br />\nHigh Tech 揩嘢，Low Tech撈嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31826a45b9f805d91d760fb3eed2c207e12709ac","tid":2334011,"uid":187107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T04:07:24.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"93c845d6fc24bd55d2cd2c5b5b3f77b01c135427","tid":2334011,"uid":385382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7d16455cacf4c9619ae01f57b84bd178da2ce3e6","tid":2334011,"uid":838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T02:47:41.000Z","msg":"老闆只能有一個"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T05:15:06.000Z","msg":"某程度上都岩，一開始如果要同其他人合作就要分好responsibilities，咁到有咩意見分歧就由個person in charge落決定，咁樣之後有咩事就由個個人負責"},{"pid":"61fccda76b92190edd64bc00650f3c7150ef8d24","tid":2334011,"uid":385382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b07abfe5bbc4add4a62c23039330e5f99c977ee6","tid":2334011,"uid":12223